OL,3,CGrandfather 'disgusted' in himself for
OL,4,Cneglect of toddler, murder trial hears
OL,6,FA man accused of murdering his two-
OL,7,Fyear-old grandson has admitted being
OL,8,Fcruel and neglectful to the toddler,
OL,9,Fand told a court he was "disgusted" in
OL,10,Fhimself.
OL,12,FMichael Ives, 47, denied he or his
OL,13,Fwife Kerry Ives, 46, inflicted a
OL,14,Fsevere head injury on Ethan Ives-
OL,15,FGriffiths before he collapsed at their
OL,16,Fhome in Flintshire, north Wales, on 14
OL,17,FAugust 2021.
