OL,3,CGrandfather 'disgusted' in himself for
OL,4,Cneglect of toddler, murder trial hears
OL,6,FEthan, who had been staying at his
OL,7,Fgrandparents' house in Garden City
OL,8,Fwith his mother Shannon Ives, 28, died
OL,9,Fin hospital two days later having
OL,10,Fsuffered catastrophic head injuries, a
OL,11,Fjury has heard.
OL,13,FUnder cross-examination by Caroline
OL,14,FRees KC, prosecuting, at Mold Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Tuesday, Ives said he felt
OL,16,F"sick" about letting Ethan decline
OL,17,Fwhile he lived with them.
