OL,3,CGrandfather 'disgusted' in himself for
OL,4,Cneglect of toddler, murder trial hears
OL,6,FHe accepted that he neglected Ethan
OL,7,Fand that the way he carried him, by
OL,8,Fhis upper arm, was cruel ` but he
OL,9,Fdenied mistreating him in other ways.
OL,11,FMs Rees said: "You were cruel and
OL,12,Fneglectful of Ethan?"
OL,14,FIves replied: "Yeah."
OL,16,FAfter watching CCTV footage of himself
OL,17,Fand Ethan in the back garden of the
OL,18,Fhome on 4 August 2021, when he could
OL,19,Fbe seen carrying the toddler by his
OL,20,Farm, Ives was asked how he felt about
OL,21,Fhow he behaved.
